name: Feather Icons (full collection)
description:
Feather is a popular collection of beautiful open source icons with an emphasis on simplicity, consistency, and flexibility.


The full Figma library is now available:

286 icons · 24×24 grid · 2px stroke


Have suggestions? Leave a comment here or let me know on Twitter.


If you’ve found this library useful, touch the ♡ at the top of the page to show your love. Thanks!


Credits: Feather icons by Cole Bemis
